# Claude Code framework (per-developer, not committed)
.claude/worktrees/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.drift-state
.claude/telemetry/
# Framework-self mode flag — present only in the upstream framework repo.
# Consumers must not have this; see .claude/framework/self/README.md.
.claude/framework-self.flag

# Code graph indexes
.code-review-graph/
.codegraph/

# Dependencies & build (adapt to your stack)
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/

# Secrets (never commit)
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Framework update system — ephemeral flag file (now lives under .claude/).
.claude/.framework-update-available.md
# apply-update staging dir (removed by trap; survives only a hard kill).
.claude/.update-staging.*
# Skills sync — ephemeral "skills behind upstream" flag (skills-check.sh).
.claude/.skills-update-available.md
# Skills sync — ephemeral non-adopter suggestion flag (skills-check.sh).
# NOTE: .claude/.skills-declined is deliberately NOT ignored — it's a
# committed project decision every clone should see.
.claude/.skills-suggestion.md

# Framework insights — ephemeral alert flag file.
.claude/.framework-insight-alert.md

# Framework doctor — ephemeral findings file.
.claude/.framework-doctor-findings.md

# verify-deps hook — ephemeral findings file (per-edit dependency check).
.claude/.dep-verification-issues.md

# instinct-miner — ephemeral session-correction candidates, proposed for
# approval at /wrapup. Never committed; deleted once triaged.
.claude/.instinct-candidates.md

# /security rotated findings archive — same pattern as review-findings/.
.claude/security-findings/
.claude/security-findings.md

# Council deliberations — local artefacts (transcripts, HTML reports, intermediate phase files).
# Each /council run writes to .claude/council/<run-id>/.
.claude/council/

# /healthcheck rotated findings archive — each run rotates the prior
# review-findings.md to .claude/review-findings/<timestamp>.md before
# starting fresh (BUG-001 fix). Archive is local audit history only.
# NOTE (deliberate asymmetry): the flat .claude/review-findings.md stays
# TRACKED — checkpoint commits of the current audit are part of the
# workflow. Only the rotated archive directory is ignored. Don't "fix"
# this by ignoring the flat file.
.claude/review-findings/
